AimRare Hub v6.5 is a client-side utility script for Roblox, providing a customizable legit-style aimbot, ESP visual tools, and a modern Fluent UI interface.
This version introduces improved performance, prediction-based aiming, and a redesigned Fluent UI.

Note: This script requires an executor that supports the Drawing API.

Key Features
üéØ Legit Aimbot

FOV-based target selection

Smooth camera interpolation (legit-style aim assist)

Hit chance simulation

Velocity-based aim prediction

Multiple aim parts (Head, UpperTorso, HumanoidRootPart)

Hold or toggle aiming modes

Optional wall-check using raycasting

Team and alive checks

üëÅ ESP System

Full player visualization system including:

Box ESP

Skeleton ESP (R15 + R6 support)

Name & Distance ESP

Health Bar ESP

Team Check for filtering teammates

ESP elements are cached for performance and updated every frame.

üñ• Fluent UI Integration

A modern Fluent-based interface with:

Three main tabs:

Legit Aim

Visuals

Settings

Real-time configurable parameters

Watermark toggle

"Unload Script" button for full cleanup

Accent color and dark-theme UI

The UI library is loaded remotely from GitHub.

